&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Education: Bachelor’s Degree (B.A.) from a four-year college or university with a major in Fashion Design is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical Skills: * Working knowledge and mastery of Adobe Illustrator and Photoshop are required for creating technical sketches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with or a strong ability to learn advanced design technology and systems (e.g., PLM systems, Ned Graphics).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong willingness and aptitude to learn and implement new computer technology, specifically 3-D design software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
