&lt;p&gt;Qualifications:&lt;br&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Business, Math, or Finance preferred.&lt;br&gt;Proven knowledge and strong proficiency in Microsoft Excel is required.&lt;br&gt;Strong analytical skills with the ability to interpret data, identify trends, and translate them into actionable insights for inventory and sales.&lt;br&gt;Exceptional organizational skills and meticulous attention to detail, especially when handling data.&lt;br&gt;Effective written and verbal communication skills for clear collaboration with team members.&lt;/p&gt;
