&lt;h2 data-path-to-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Human Resource Manager – Miami Headquarters&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Role Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot;&gt;We are seeking an experienced Human Resource Manager to lead HR operations at our Miami Headquarters. This role focuses heavily on strengthening employee relations, maintaining total labor compliance, and streamlining core HR operations for our corporate team. Additionally, you will provide general HR support and oversight for our Miami warehouse workforce.&amp;nbsp;The ideal candidate will be a trusted, high-level HR partner who can confidently resolve complex employee relations matters, manage intricate immigration cases, and ensure a smooth operational experience for all team members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Employee Relations:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the primary champion for a positive and compliant workplace culture. Conduct objective investigations, proactively mitigate conflicts, and design strategies that support employee retention, equity, and fair treatment across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Core HR Operations:&lt;/strong&gt; Standardize and manage foundational HR lifecycle processes, including structured onboarding/offboarding, performance management frameworks, benefits administration, and regular HR audits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Immigration &amp;amp; Visa Processing:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage the end-to-end lifecycle of H-1B visas and other employment-based visa workflows. Partner with external immigration counsel, track strict compliance timelines, and guide foreign national employees through the intake and renewal processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
