&lt;li&gt;Participate in maintaining consistency of technical design and product creation processes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with OVS offices and Direct Vendor Technical teams to ensure execution of fit, construction and finishing&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure Brand consistency in aesthetic, fit and construction from vendor to vendor across all styles within a category&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively communicate with cross functional teams to ensure calendar milestone deliverables are met&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify and solve potential production, quality and costing issues and make appropriate recommendations for resolutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate issues when necessary and provide root cause analysis, fact finding and possible solutions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track workload deliverables to ensure individual deadlines are met and work with production partners to avoid garment delivery slides.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend key Milestone meetings to provide technical support with regards to fit and construction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fosters open communication and team environment with all business partners and receives constructive feedback professionally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise direct reports as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
